@startuml
title 系统架构图
hide footbox
actor 用户
participant "MCP Client" as Client
participant "PlantUML Server" as Server
database "文件系统" as FS

用户 -> Client: 发送PlantUML文本
Client -> Server: 调用render_plantuml
Server -> Server: 解析PlantUML
Server -> Server: 生成图像
Server -> FS: 保存图像文件
Server -> Client: 返回结果(路径+base64)
Client -> 用户: 显示图像

@enduml
